🛍️ Customer Segmentation

📌 Objective
Cluster customers into groups based on their **Annual Income** and **Spending Score**.

📊 Dataset
    - Mall Customer Dataset (Kaggle)
    - Features: Income, Spending Score

🔧 Steps Taken
    - Data scaling for clustering
    - Exploratory Data Analysis (scatterplots, distributions)
    - K-Means clustering applied
    - Elbow Method used to find optimal clusters
    - Visualized clusters in 2D plots

🏆 Results
    - Customers segmented into different groups (e.g., High Income–High Spending, Low Income–Low Spending, etc.)
    - Useful for targeted marketing strategies

🎯 Bonus
    - Implemented DBSCAN clustering for comparison
    - Analyzed average spending per cluster
